### ==========================================
### AI 能力模块 API 测试
### ==========================================

### 0. 获取 Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "XiyuAdmin2026!"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. 正常流程：获取 AI 配置
GET http://localhost:18081/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 正常流程：测试 AI 连接
POST http://localhost:18081/api/settings/ai-models/test
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openai",
  "model": "gpt-4"
}

### 3. 正常流程：获取 AI 分析
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders/1/match-score/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 正常流程：AI 评分历史
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders/1/match-score/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 正常流程：AI 最新评分
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders/1/match-score/latest
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 正常流程：知识库搜索（AI 方案检索用）
GET http://localhost:18081/api/knowledge/cases?page=0&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 边界：不存在的标讯 AI 分析
GET http://localhost:18081/api/tenders/999999/match-score/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
